				imagePath='/src/assets/heymath.png'
				altText='Umesh, Software Engineer, HeyMath'
				imageClass='h-12 w-auto md:-left-20'
				href='https://www.heymath.com'
			>
				HeyMath! is an educational technology company focused on mathematics education using
				animated and interactive visual/video lesson content.
