				quickly became one of the lead developers. In this role, I contributed significantly to
				lesson and content management platforms, an online test engine, and a school platform where students can access content.
				Additionally, I took on the responsibility of being the release manager for the entire
				tech products. MY experience further expanded during the later stages of my tenure, where
				I was involved in some major tech infrastructure changes, including the migration from
				baremetal to VPS, moving apps from windoes to linux environments. I was also of a team which did an innovative project for offline content distribution
				in South Africa. -->
			</Card>
